sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Backend API
    participant SE as SearchEngine
    participant LLM as Ollama
    participant DB as MongoDB

    U->>FE: Submit query
    FE->>API: POST /ask { query, use_llm }
    activate API
    API->>API: Validate & init

    API->>SE: Search + score + rerank
    activate SE
    SE-->>API: Top articles
    deactivate SE

    opt LLM available
        API->>API: Truncate + format prompt
        API->>LLM: Generate answer
        activate LLM
        LLM-->>API: Answer
        deactivate LLM
    end

    API->>DB: Persist
    activate DB
    DB-->>API: Done
    deactivate DB
    API-->>FE: 200 + results
    deactivate API
    FE-->>U: Display results
